<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Marquess" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Marquess,</orth> a title of honour, next below that of duke: <bibl n="shak. mv 1.2.125" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 2, 125</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.15" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.15" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 15</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.164" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 3, 164</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.255" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 255</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.255" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 255</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.2.47" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 47</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 4.1.38" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 IV, 1, 38</bibl>. <cit><quote>lord m.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.63" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 63</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.1.25" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 1, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.520" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 520</bibl>. Used as a fem.: <cit><quote>Lady M. Dorset,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.170" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 170</bibl></cit>.
